Package: libevent
Section: libs
Priority: optional
Architecture: ARCH
Depends: libc (>= 1.1.8), ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: provides functions for asynchronous event notification
 The libevent API provides a mechanism to execute a callback function
 when a specific event occurs on a file descriptor or after a timeout
 has been reached. Furthermore, libevent also support callbacks due to 
 signals or regular timeouts.
 .
 This package provides libevent shared libraries.

Package: libevent-dev
Section: libdevel
Priority: optional
Architecture: ARCH
Depends: libevent (= ${binary:Version}), openssl-dev
Description: Development headers and static libraries for libevent
 This package provides libevent-1.0.a, pkgconfig data and
 header files required for development using libevent.
